<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> الثَّانِيَةُ: المُتَوَفَّى عَنْهَا بِلَا حَمْلٍ؛<span class="c5"> فَتَعْتَدُّ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> حُرَّةٌ:</span> أَرْبَعَةَ أَشْهُرٍ وَعَشْرَ لَيَالٍ بِعَشَرَةِ أَيَّامٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَمَةٌ:</span> نِصْفَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمُبَعَّضَةٌ:</span> بِالحِسَابِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَعْتَدُّ مَنْ أَبَانَهَا فِي مَرَضِ مَوْتِهِ:</span> الأَطْوَلَ مِنْ عِدَّةِ وَفَاةٍ أَوْ طَلَاقٍ إِنْ وَرِثَتْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَإِلَّا عِدَّةَ طَلَاقٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> الثَّالِثَةُ: ذَاتُ الحَيْضِ المُفَارَقَةُ فِي الحَيَاةِ:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَتَعْتَدُّ حُرَّةٌ وَمُبَعَّضَةٌ:</span> بِثَلَاثِ حَيْضَاتٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَمَةٌ:</span> بِحَيْضَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> الرَّابِعَةُ: المُفَارَقَةُ فِي الحَيَاةِ،<span class="c5"> وَلَمْ تَحِضْ لِصِغَرٍ أَوْ إِيَاسٍ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَتَعْتَدُّ حُرَّةٌ:</span> بِثَلَاثَةِ أَشْهُرٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَمَةٌ:</span> بِشَهْرَيْنِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمُبَعَّضَةٌ:</span> بِالحِسَابِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> الخَامِسَةُ: مَنِ ارْتَفَعَ حَيْضُهَا:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَمْ تَعْلَمْ مَا رَفَعَهُ:</span> فَتَعْتَدُّ لِلْحَمْلِ غَالِبَ مُدَّتِهِ، ثُمَّ تَعْتَدُّ كَآيِسَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>